<section class="section section--alt" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <span class="section__tag">Oddiy jarayon</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">3 qadam — 2 daqiqa</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">Dasturchi bo'lish shart emas. Hech narsa yozish kerak emas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">1</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">Bot yarating va tokenini yuboring</h3>
          <p class="step__text">Telegram'da @BotFather orqali bot yarating. Olingan tokenni Getolog botiga yuboring — biz tekshirib olamiz.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step__line"></div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">2</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">Sozlamalarni belgilang</h3>
          <p class="step__text">Kanal/guruhni ulang, narx qo'ying, muddat belgilang (1/6/12 oy yoki umrbod), karta raqamingizni kiriting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step__line"></div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__number">3</div>
        <div class="step__body">
          <h3 class="step__title">Bot ishlaydi — pul tushadi</h3>
          <p class="step__text">Botingiz 24/7 ishlaydi. Foydalanuvchilar to'lov qiladi, avtomatik invite link oladi. Siz faqat kuzatasiz.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step__number {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    min-width: 52px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .step__body {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .step__title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .step__text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--light-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .step__line {
    width: 2px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), transparent);
    margin-left: 25px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
</style>
